title: Staples CD Labeler V5 - ISO
description:
Staples CD Labeler V5 Software


The Software can install as English or French

The Staples CD Labeling software V5 is not only used with Staples CD/DVD Labels but is 

Compatible with the Avery 5931/8931 Labels

Minimum System Requirements
. Windows XP, Windows Vista, Windows 7
. 1GB Ram (2GB recommended for Vista and Windows 7)
. 250 MB available harddrive space
. 800 x 600 Monitor resolution (1024x768 recommended)
. Windows compatible inkjet or Laser printer

Note: CD Labeling software not use with Mac OS.
